Class Autonomous

    edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.NamedSendable, edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.Sendable

    public class Autonomous
extends edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.command.CommandGroup
    Command group that is run automatically when the robot enters autonomous mode. This year, it will drive to the line of RCs, grab 'em, and put them on the lower conveyor belt, all while plowing totes out of the way with the plower. There is a discussion on GitHub about this command.
